quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  33,53,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimwinjire mumazu y’intumwa y’Imana kugeza aho muhabwa uruhusha rwukuja gufungura, nukutarindira kugeza aho ivyo bifungurwa bihira, mugabo ni mwaba mufise ubutumire aho niho murekuriwe kwinjira, kandi muhejeje gufungura nimuce mwitahira mutarinze gushinga ibiyago kuko ibintu nk’ivyo vyamye bishavuza intumwa y’Imana, nawe aho ari akagira isoni, mugabo Imana ntibona isoni ivugishije ukuri, namwe mugihe mubajije abapfasoni biwe nimubabarize inyuma y’uruzitiro, kugira gutyo n’ugusukura imitima yanyu hamwe n’imitima yabo, kandi sivyiza gushavuza intumwa y’Imana canke kwubakana n’abapfasoni biwe munyuma yiwe, rero kugira gutyo kizoba ari igicumuro kininiya cane imbere y’Imana"
  33,54,"Nimwa serura icarico cose canke mukaki nyegeza, ntimuzi yuko Imana ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  33,55,"Ntagicumuro kuribo no kuri badata babo, canke kubibondo vyabo, canke bene wabo, canke kubana babene babo, canke abana babashiki babo, canke abakenyezi nkabo, canke bamwe bitungiwe n’amaboko yabo y’iburyo, nimutinye Imana yanyu mwebwe bakenyezi kuko ntankeka Imana niyo cabona kiri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  33,56,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana imanura imigisha kuntumwa yayo hamwe no kuba marayika bayo, rero mwebwe aba Isilamu kandi muyisengere intumwa y’Imana muyisabira amahoro y’Imana n’imigisha nukumusabira amahoro"
  33,57,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bashavuza Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo, abo bantu Imana yarabavumye kuri iy’Isi no mw’ijuru, kandi yaraba teguriye ibihano bibatetereza"
  33,58,"Nabarya bashavuza abagabo baba Isilamu hamwe n’abakenyezi babo ata n’ikosa narimwe bagize, ntankeka abo bantu nabikoreye ubuhemu buniniya hamwe n’ibicumuro biri k’umugaragaro"